              <title>Maitreyopaniṣad</title>
              <title type="vernacular">मैत्रेयोपनिषद्</title>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti maitreyyupaniṣa[dādi] samāptā // śrīśaṃkarārpaṇam astu // (f. 2r).</colophon>
